Interface IEditableCloudLabelProvider

All Superinterfaces:
IBaseLabelProvider, ICloudLabelProvider
All Known Implementing Classes:
TypeLabelProvider
public interface IEditableCloudLabelProvider extends ICloudLabelProvider
An IEditableCloudLabelProvider is supported by the CloudOptionsComposite, such that it can be used to modify colors, fonts, and angles.
